Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class SlimGameModel

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.SlimGameModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SlimGameModel extends Object implements Serializable
Represents the model in a "slimmer" way. Used when after the initialization phase of the game and when a client reconnects, after quitting the game, and asks to be updated on the game status. A new SlimGameModel object is built every time a clients asks for a reconnection.
